'''Kōtaijingū''' (皇大神宮) is a {{ill|Shinto shrine|ja|神社}} that enshrines {{ill|Amaterasu-ōmikami|ja|天照大御神}}.
==List== * {{ill|Kōtaijingū|ja|皇大神宮}} - Located in {{ill|Ise|ja|伊勢市}}, {{ill|Mie Prefecture|ja|三重県}}. The Inner Shrine (Naikū) of {{ill|Ise Grand Shrine|ja|伊勢神宮}}. * {{ill|Iseyama Kōtaijingū|ja|伊勢山皇大神宮}} - Located in {{ill|Nishi-ku, Yokohama|ja|西区 (横浜市)}}, {{ill|Yokohama|ja|横浜市}}, {{ill|Kanagawa Prefecture|ja|神奈川県}}. * {{ill|Kōtaijingū (Fujisawa)|ja|皇大神宮 (藤沢市)}} - Located in {{ill|Fujisawa|ja|藤沢市}}, Kanagawa Prefecture. * {{ill|Kōtaijingū (Osaka)|ja|皇大神宮 (大阪市)}} - Located in {{ill|Jōtō-ku, Osaka|ja|城東区}}, {{ill|Osaka|ja|大阪市}}, {{ill|Osaka Prefecture|ja|大阪府}}, specifically in {{ill|Imafuku Minami|ja|今福南}}. * {{ill|Kōtaijingū (Ishii)|ja|皇大神宮 (石井町)}} - Located in {{ill|Ishii|ja|石井町}}, {{ill|Myōzai District|ja|名西郡}}, {{ill|Tokushima Prefecture|ja|徳島県}}. * {{ill|Amaterasu Kōtaijingū|ja|天照皇大神宮}} - Located in {{ill|Hisayama|ja|久山町}}, {{ill|Kasuya District|ja|糟屋郡}}, {{ill|Fukuoka Prefecture|ja|福岡県}}. * {{ill|Urakami Kōtaijingū|ja|浦上皇大神宮}} - Located in {{ill|Nagasaki|ja|長崎市}}, {{ill|Nagasaki Prefecture|ja|長崎県}}. → {{ill|Sannō Shrine (Nagasaki)|ja|山王神社 (長崎市)}}
==See also== * {{ill|Shimmei Shrine|ja|神明神社}} * {{ill|Amaterasu Kōtaijingū-kyō|ja|天照皇大神宮教}}
