The Main shrine is the {{ill|Kōtai Jingū|ja|皇大神宮|1=Kōtai Jingū|2=ja|3=皇大神宮|4=zh|5=皇大神宮|qq=draft}} of [[Ise Grand Shrines]] and shrines with the same name are Branch shrines of that shrine. Similar to shrines called {{ill|Daijingū|ja|大神宮|qq=draft}}. While {{ill|Jingu|ja|神宮|qq=draft}} is a highly prestigious title limited to only a few shrines. Kotai Jingus and Daijingus (皇大神宮 and 大神宮) are often much less prestigious and have that title by virtue of being branch shrines of a highly prestigious shrine
==List== * {{ill|Kōtai Jingū|ja|皇大神宮|1=Kōtai Jingū|2=ja|3=皇大神宮|4=zh|5=皇大神宮|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Ise|ja|伊勢市|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Mie Prefecture|ja|三重県|qq=draft}}. The Inner Shrine (Naikū) of {{ill|Ise Grand Shrine|ja|伊勢神宮|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Iseyama Kōtai Jingu|ja伊勢山皇大神宮|1=Iseyama Kōtai Jingū|2=fr|3=Iseyama Kotai Jingu|4=ja|5=伊勢山皇大神宮|6=zh|7=伊勢山皇大神宮|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Nishi-ku, Yokohama|ja|西区 (横浜市)|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Yokohama|ja|横浜市|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Kanagawa Prefecture|ja|神奈川県|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Kotai Jingu (Fujisawa City)|ja|皇大神宮 (藤沢市)|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Fujisawa|ja|藤沢市|qq=draft}}, Kanagawa Prefecture. * {{ill|Kōtaijingū (Osaka)|ja|皇大神宮 (大阪市)|1=Kōtai Jingū (Osaka)|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Jōtō-ku, Osaka|ja|城東区|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Osaka|ja|大阪市|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Osaka Prefecture|ja|大阪府|qq=draft}}, specifically in {{ill|Imafuku Minami|ja|今福南|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Kōtai Jingū (Ishii)|ja|皇大神宮 (石井町)|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Ishii|ja|石井町|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Myōzai District|ja|名西郡|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Tokushima Prefecture|ja|徳島県|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Amaterasu Kōtaijingū|ja伊勢山皇大神宮|1=Tenshō Kōtai Jingū|2=ja|3=天照皇大神宮|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Hisayama|ja|久山町|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Kasuya District|ja|糟屋郡|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Fukuoka Prefecture|ja|福岡県|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Urakami Kōtaijingū|ja|浦上皇大神宮|1=Kōtai Jingū|2=ja|3=皇大神宮|4=zh|5=皇大神宮|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Nagasaki|ja|長崎市|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Nagasaki Prefecture|ja|長崎県|qq=draft}}. → {{ill|Sannō Shrine (Nagasaki)|ja|山王神社 (長崎市)|qq=draft}}
==See also== * [[Shinmei shrines]] * {{ill|Daijingū|ja|大神宮|qq=draft}} * {{ill|Tenshō Kōtai Jingūkyō|ja|天照皇大神宮教|qq=draft}} * {{ill|Kōtai Shrine|ja|皇大神社|qq=draft}} * {{ill|Tenso Shrine|ja|天祖神社 (曖昧さ回避)|zh|天祖神社|qq=draft}} * [[Kotai_Shrine_(disambiguation)]]
